io.github.prolobjectlink.db

Interface StoragePool

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, Container, Defragtable, PersistentContainer, Restorable, Transactional, Wrapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractStoragePool, PrologStoragePool

    public interface StoragePool
extends PersistentContainer
    Container folder that have many single storages with limited clauses for each storage in a located root folder.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
    See Also:
    Storage, StorageManager
